[
  {
    "startTime": 0.266,
    "endTime": 2.68,
    "text": "Now I thought I'd share some of my favorite"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 2.68,
    "endTime": 3.67,
    "text": "MyFamilyIsWeird stories from you guys."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 3.67,
    "endTime": 6.84,
    "text": "This first one is from @Kimjohnston."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 6.84,
    "endTime": 8.708,
    "text": "He says..."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 8.8,
    "endTime": 12.0,
    "text": "My dad once dumped his chocolate milkshake on the hood of my brother's Jeep because"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 12.0,
    "endTime": 15.0,
    "text": "\"if we're going through the car wash, we may as well get our money's worth.\""
  },
  {
    "startTime": 19.686,
    "endTime": 26.259999999999998,
    "text": "This one's from @lea22089. She says..."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 26.3,
    "endTime": 29.0,
    "text": "My grandmother has fake plants but she likes to use real dirt to make them seem real."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 31.531,
    "endTime": 32.766,
    "text": "That is weird."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 32.766,
    "endTime": 34.333,
    "text": "That is weird."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 34.334,
    "endTime": 37.303000000000004,
    "text": "This one's from @Mariabarnes96."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 37.303,
    "endTime": 39.272,
    "text": "She said..."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 39.3,
    "endTime": 43.0,
    "text": "When we can't find parking at a restaurant, my dad parks in the \"Carry Out\" parking spots."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 43.0,
    "endTime": 44.6,
    "text": "He says it still counts because we'll be \"carrying out\" the food in our stomachs."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 49.616,
    "endTime": 50.717,
    "text": "Not sexy."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 50.717,
    "endTime": 53.153,
    "text": "This one's from @garrettsatfield."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 53.153,
    "endTime": 54.32,
    "text": "I like that name."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 54.32,
    "endTime": 56.623,
    "text": "Garrett Satfield."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 56.623,
    "endTime": 58.724,
    "text": "Sounds like somebody I'd be friends with."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 59.926,
    "endTime": 61.795,
    "text": "I went out to dinner the other night"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 61.795,
    "endTime": 63.863,
    "text": "with Garrett Satfield. -How is Garrett?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 63.863,
    "endTime": 64.664,
    "text": "He's fantastic as always."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 64.664,
    "endTime": 66.66,
    "text": "He's just a positive dude, always nice."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 66.66,
    "endTime": 68.67999999999999,
    "text": "-That's good. -Happy -- he's married."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 68.68,
    "endTime": 70.13600000000001,
    "text": "-Wife is lovely. -Wife is great, too."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 70.136,
    "endTime": 71.704,
    "text": "-Linda is lovely. -Yeah."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 71.704,
    "endTime": 73.205,
    "text": "We're having the Satfields over for dinner..."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 73.206,
    "endTime": 73.973,
    "text": "-Are you really? -...again"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 73.973,
    "endTime": 75.908,
    "text": "'cause I had so much fun last night."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 75.909,
    "endTime": 76.509,
    "text": "Oh, my gosh."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 76.509,
    "endTime": 77.911,
    "text": "I'm going to do it every night of the week."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 77.911,
    "endTime": 79.145,
    "text": "Oh, my gosh. He's so fun."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 79.145,
    "endTime": 79.913,
    "text": "You know how much fun he is?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 79.913,
    "endTime": 82.82,
    "text": "-Who? You talking about GS? -Yeah, GS."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 82.715,
    "endTime": 84.284,
    "text": "Garrett Man. The gangster."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 84.284,
    "endTime": 85.31800000000001,
    "text": "Yeah, he's fantastic."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 85.318,
    "endTime": 87.87,
    "text": "Yeah, I just love Garrett Satfield."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 87.87,
    "endTime": 88.321,
    "text": "Really? How much do you love him?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 88.321,
    "endTime": 93.158,
    "text": "Well, I mean, I love my wife and my kids."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 93.159,
    "endTime": 96.129,
    "text": "But above all, Gary Statfield."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 97.764,
    "endTime": 99.466,
    "text": "He says..."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 99.5,
    "endTime": 101.0,
    "text": "My grandpa liked to sit in his chair with a blanket and no pants."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 101.0,
    "endTime": 103.0,
    "text": "When he got up, he'd yell, \"Red light!\" and we'd have to close our eyes."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 103.0,
    "endTime": 108.0,
    "text": "When he thought we was far enough down the hall, he'd yell, \"Green light!\""
  },
  {
    "startTime": 108.0,
    "endTime": 110.0,
    "text": "He was never far enough."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 112.178,
    "endTime": 113.346,
    "text": "Grandpa!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 113.346,
    "endTime": 116.916,
    "text": "Grandpa, we're at yellow right now."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 116.916,
    "endTime": 119.786,
    "text": "Take the blanket with you."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 119.786,
    "endTime": 122.755,
    "text": "\"I'm about to go yellow.\""
  },
  {
    "startTime": 122.755,
    "endTime": 124.624,
    "text": "Is that right?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 124.624,
    "endTime": 125.324,
    "text": "Brown light."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 125.325,
    "endTime": 127.12700000000001,
    "text": "Brown light, that's..."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 130.797,
    "endTime": 133.32,
    "text": "This one's from @Danimichelle."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 133.32,
    "endTime": 134.801,
    "text": "She says..."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 134.9,
    "endTime": 138.0,
    "text": "When I was learning to parallel park, my dad used my sister and brother as traffic cones."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 140.907,
    "endTime": 143.209,
    "text": "Yay, dad. Get your money's worth."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 143.209,
    "endTime": 146.546,
    "text": "Now we learn how to drive to the hospital."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 146.546,
    "endTime": 147.79,
    "text": "Here we go."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 147.8,
    "endTime": 151.751,
    "text": "This one's from @etess97. She says..."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 151.8,
    "endTime": 155.0,
    "text": "I once heard my grandparents giggling upstairs and when I walked past their bedroom,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 155.0,
    "endTime": 157.0,
    "text": "I saw them wearing each others' dentures."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 161.6,
    "endTime": 163.429,
    "text": "What?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 163.429,
    "endTime": 164.16400000000002,
    "text": "How would you know?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 164.164,
    "endTime": 166.266,
    "text": "I mean, they're not even my grandparents,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 166.266,
    "endTime": 167.534,
    "text": "and I want to unsee that."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 167.534,
    "endTime": 170.69,
    "text": "Oh, green light!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 170.69,
    "endTime": 175.375,
    "text": "The last one's from @crusty316. He says..."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 175.4,
    "endTime": 179.0,
    "text": "To save money my dad used to bring us to the Disney section at Toys 'R Us and say, \"Welcome to Disneyland!\""
  },
  {
    "startTime": 179.779,
    "endTime": 180.513,
    "text": "There you have it."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 180.513,
    "endTime": 182.348,
    "text": "Those are our \"Tonight Show hashtags.\""
  },
  {
    "startTime": 182.348,
    "endTime": 183.85000000000002,
    "text": "To check out more of our favorites,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 183.85,
    "endTime": 186.386,
    "text": "go to tonightshow.com/hashtags."
  }
]